summary: This Mod is a representation of the Drow Race.  It contains Powers unique to the Drow Race.
descriptionHtml:
[color=aqua]
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Version 1.4.0
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
[/color][color=orange]
This Mod is a representation of the Drow Race. It contains Powers unique to the Drow Race.

If you like this Mod, please Endorse it as it makes all the hours of effort worthwhile :-)

Some Screenshots would also be great..!

Note: - This Race fully supports the excellent "ApachiiSkyHair " Mod which can found here: -

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168

Two of the Screenshots are using the ApachiiSkyHair Female from the above.

[/color][color=aqua]
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Updates
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
[/color][color=orange]
v1.1.6 - Added CHSBHC Female Body Support, Updated the CBBE Textures to v3.2 and Racial Compatibility options updated.
v1.1.5 - NMM Installation with all options included and Dawnguard Support.
v1.1.4 - Optional Component - Integration of Handsome Male Elves and Humans - Young.
v1.1.3 - Optional Component - Integration of Handsome Male Elves and Humans - Mature.
v1.1.2 - Merged Optional Components and Integrated Xenius Character Enhancements.
v1.1.1 - Added ADEC Female Body Support.
v1.1.0 - Integration with "Creating a Playable Race - The Right Way".
v1.0.2 - DIMONIZED UNP Female Body (Main) - Body Spider & Web Tattoo Addon.
v1.0.1 - DIMONIZED UNP Female Body (Main) Support Added.
v1.0.0 - Initial Vanilla and CBBE Female Body Support.
[/color][color=aqua]
/////////////////
Racial Abilities
/////////////////
[/color][color=red]
Drow Weakness to Sunlight -
A Drow's Health, Magicka, and Stamina recover to a slower (20%) extent while exposed to Sunlight. They are also reduced by 10 points.[/color][color=green]
Dark Mother's Birthright - 25% Resistance to Disease, Magic & Poison.
Dark Mother's Birthright - Drow Have 25 More Magicka.
[/color][color=aqua]
/////////////////
Racial Powers
/////////////////
[/color][color=green]
Dark Mother's Veil - Drow have a Power that grants Ghost Veil and Fortifies Sneak by 50%.
Dark Mother's Eye - Drow have a Lesser Power that grants Night Eye.
Dark Mother's Light - Drow have a Lesser Power that grants Light.
[/color][color=aqua]
/////////////////
Racial Skills
/////////////////
[/color][color=green]
Destruction +5
Restoration +5
One-Handed +5
Two-Handed +5
Block +5
Light Armor +5
Heavy Armor +5
[/color][color=aqua]

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Credits
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
[/color]
